The map will allow you to assess your knowledge of the island. The roads you have traveled are marked in a bright color. Taking these unfamiliar routes will enable you to discover the game modes, the showrooms, the houses and much much more...

Note that by choosing different tabs with [LB] [RB], you can access different groups of locations. You are currently looking at the locations types "races".  The blue icons represent the SINGLE PLAYER races, the orange icons indicate MULTIPLAYER races.

The locations selected indicate different stores on the island. Familiarize yourself with their icon. Remember that you can filter the display of the locations, which will be very useful when you have discovered a large number of them.

You can use this tab to locate the position of the players on your friends list. You can only join a friend if you have discovered the zone where he is located.
Using maximum zoom out with [LT], you will see the whole island and the locations of all the players in the TEST DRIVE community.

You are now familiar with the TEST DRIVE environment. You can go and explore the island!  On your travels, note the holograph icons above the roads. Learn to recognize them immediately; some will gain you entry to races where you can win prize money and others are stores.  
Enjoy!
